Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Oath of Wind {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}and Water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Oath of Wind {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}and Water
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:39.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:39.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}Sword of the Holy Man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:02.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\fs40\pos(640,450)}Three years earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ruby of Wind, passed down through the Albion Kingdom, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Ruby of Water, passed down through the Tristain Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water and wind create a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rainbow between the two royal families.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let there be a rainbow between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those who are in the midst of forbidden love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit that lives in Lagdorian Lake is also called the Spirit of Oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been told that an oath made here cannot be torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a fairy tale, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Henrietta of the Tristain Kingdom, hereby make an oath to the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will love Prince Wales for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, will you please swear your love, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Prince Wales of the Albion Kingdom,\Nhereby make an oath to the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To walk along the side of this Lagdorian Lake while holding Princess Henrietta of Tristain's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...under the bright sun without worrying the eyes of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I live in a world where you don't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rainbow can only exist in the sky in the presence of both water and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent man, coming to the Queen's room after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is me, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the window for me, my dear Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cannot be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not dead, for I am alive before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who died was my double.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall show you the proof that I am really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that windy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The oath between the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come for you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Albion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to Albion now, they will definitely kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I must return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my duty as a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay in this kingdom with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the story behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess got kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinates are currently on the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruffian who kidnapped Her Highness is headed towards Lagdorian Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagdorian Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we cannot publicise this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must save Her Highness with only my Musketeer Force and you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will cooperate, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crisis involved the Princess, so we can't overlook this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still under repair, do you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need it to do is fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Colbert-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the thing I asked you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean the acceleration unit that uses gunpowder, I had it installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should let you take off even with a short runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, it's no time for chitchat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to catch up with Agnes fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these parts left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's with the racket so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Princess got kidnapped from the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of that, she said that she\Nthought there was a spy in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ring of Andvari was also stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was supposed to be returned to the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before doing that the castle was holding on to it temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, Montmo said it's a magical item that gives the dead a false life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the use for such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, it's for controlling the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, we need to catch up with them fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't this go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the Spirit of Water was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...drawn up to the surface by the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have become beautiful, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are more beautiful than the Spirit of Water herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are almost at the place of our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagdorian Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagdorian...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a ship hidden by the lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will fly to the Albion using that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let anyone interfere with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must catch up and save Her Highness as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I see Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out, Michel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim at the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not hit Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my Musketeer Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not want anyone to interfere with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain everything to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just be quiet and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is act according to those words you said when you made the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Henrietta of the Tristain Kingdom,\Nhereby make an oath to the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will love Wales-sama for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us speak our oath by the lakeside again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Prince Wales of Albion, will love Henrietta for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, this might crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, crash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you stupid, stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to save the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, don't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it land somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.78,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Kirche's here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't think we deserve that after saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is a secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that makes me want to follow you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Wales?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Prince should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ring of Andvari?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go. The ship is up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inescapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, is that Queen Henrietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return the Princess to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta came with me under her own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales, don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were revived with the Ring of Andvari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring of Andvari, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a magic item that gives false lives to the dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were true... it would be a frightening thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a phantom of the Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, do not speak such nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who died was Wales-sama's double!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Wales-sama himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you shall let us through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversation is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lavis fortal is hetha wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks cannot wound me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that it is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche, Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, you saw that, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a phantom with a false life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cannot be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he would love me for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly loved someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would want to follow that person, even if you had to cast away everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, let me go, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise Françoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my last order to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the sleep talking for when you're in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... isn't love or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on going,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you lay even a finger on Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, I beg you, please move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only wish to pass on by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unite the Water Triangle and the Wind Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, why not use the Book of Invocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Book of Invocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, nothing's written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dispel magic"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one. Undo the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The privilege of the selected royal family, Hexagon Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ful blisars ansul ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your job to protect your master until the spell's done, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyofu need nousis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Zero's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heilos iala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the best I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elpeo Y's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was being controlled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to forgive me for what I have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...promise me, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will promise you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What must I promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you will forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me to forget me and love another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear those words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By this Lagdorian Lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot possibly promise such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot make a false promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have time left in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please promise with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll love me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were Wales-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Wales-sama would swear, and then the oath would be made!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to, if I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the deceased cannot promise an eternity, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not say those words three years ago either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because our fate was never bound to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad that I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wales-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that windy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The oath between the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing accepting a sword battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a flamen from Romalia,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a real handsome man, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never win with {\i1}your{\i0} face
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword of the Holy Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
